---
const features = [
  "sparas i Google Sheets, Excel eller CRM",
  "skickas till rätt person",
  "bekräftas till kunden",
  "följs upp med påminnelse",
  "inkluderas i veckosammanställning",
];
---

<section id="vad-vi-gor" class="mx-auto mt-20 max-w-3xl text-center">
  <h2 class="mt-3 text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-zinc-950 lg:text-5xl">
    Varje ny förfrågan
  </h2>

  <div class="mt-8 overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-zinc-200 bg-white text-left shadow-sm shadow-zinc-200/70">
    {
      features.map((feature) => (
        <div class="flex gap-4 border-b border-zinc-200 px-5 py-4 last:border-b-0">
          <span class="mt-2 h-2.5 w-2.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-emerald-400" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <p class="text-lg font-semibold leading-7 text-zinc-800">{feature}</p>
        </div>
      ))
    }
  </div>

  <div class="mx-auto mt-8 max-w-2xl space-y-3 text-lg leading-8 text-zinc-700">
    <p>Inget stort systemprojekt.</p>
    <p>Bara mindre risk att varma leads blir liggande.</p>
  </div>
</section>
